data.description: Updates - roof (2023) impact windows/doors (2020) a/c (2017) hot water heater (2023) cast iron pipes relined w/ warranty (2020) electrical panel (2020) attic reinsulated (2020)! Discover your ideal haven in this ranch home w/ in-ground pool that harmoniously combines comfort, convenience, & tranquility. Boasting 2 beds, den/office & 2 baths, this residence offers a spacious layout. You'll be entranced by the fenced yard w/ exquisite landscaping. Pool has screened-in lanai, heated w/ owned solar panels & programmable timer. Hurricane impact windows/doors fortify the home - no need for shutters - & contribute to energy efficiency. Kitchen cabinets were replaced, accompanied by pull-out drawers & stainless steel appliances. A workshop provides storage & workspace – it can transformed into 3rd bed! The living room boasts new vinyl flooring, crown molding & built-in surround sound system & bathroom has a new tile shower, toilet & vanity. 2nd bed has en-suite bathroom & access to pool. The den/office can be used as private space for guests. Well water is used for irrigation & can be used to wash home/cars. *NO HOA *Qualifies for insurance discounts & FHA/VA loans *Handicap accessible
